<h1>Welcome to Delteria</h1>

<p>
Come enter the world of Delteria, to experience a vast MMORPG experience filled with magic and adventure! Create your own character and begin your own story! 
</p>

<p>
While engaging in a multitude of quests on your journey through the mythical worlds of Deltlite and Kaljun you will be able to:
</p>
<ul>
  <li>Encounter a variety of monsters on the overworld and engage in PvP or PvE battles!</li>
  <li>Fight up close or from afar using both melee or ranged weapons!</li>
  <li>Specialize your character with a variety of perks to boost your skills!</li>
  <li>Create or join a party/guild and explore vast dungeons to defeat a boss and gather what loot it may offer!</li>
  <li>Join a multitude of server wide events when you tire of forcing evil out of the lands of Delteria!</li>
</ul>

